{"tid":684751,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[第一人稱射擊／現代戰爭]《World War 3》釋出官方預告片","createTime":"2018-05-30T21:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T10:32:58.000Z","uid":16404,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"174c18b25fe99c16c45863ea2918c3b28047506b","tid":684751,"uid":16404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T21:11:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0r4Yr2ZnRfk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0r4Yr2ZnRfk&d=7XoLXWbv7emJM5%2BbI3wmLf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=cf0128e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0r4Yr2ZnRfk</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官方遊戲介紹：<a href=\"http://worldwar3.com/en/game-overview/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fworldwar3.com%2Fen%2Fgame-overview%2F&d=7XoLXWbv7emJM5%2BbI3wmLf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=094ce422\" target=\"_blank\">http://worldwar3.com/en/game-overview/</a><br />\n<br />\n2018會係Steam平台以Early Access推出<br />\n<br />\n隻game由 The Farm 51波蘭開發，暫時只有三張地圖，三個國家軍隊<br />\n華沙(波蘭)／柏林(德國)／莫斯科(俄羅斯)<br />\n<br />\n官網有寫 強調民族自豪感，極有可能會係未來加入多國軍隊<br />\n射擊game點可以少左美軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">同埋早幾日睇過贏国新聞 好似話入面有解放軍裝甲車</span><br />\n<br />\n極大量定制功能，<br />\n－槍械迷彩塗裝、握把、瞄準鏡、子彈類型等等等等都可以揀<br />\n(有d似Ghost Recon未來戰士)<br />\n－坦克 （定制應該都不外乎迷彩、坦克裝甲類型）<br />\n－角色制服，頭盔，防彈背心 （似Arma3）<br />\n<br />\n呢堆先可以叫做定制功能架ma<br />\n唔似得某隻垃圾game 拎住二戰個朵 <br />\n加埋d咩機械\b義肢 女兵 武士刀 藍色化妝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n官方強調 『最真實的子彈與裝甲系統』：同軍火公司，退役軍人一齊研究<br />\n避彈衣終於擋到子彈啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拿拿聲出 砌低ea啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146e7da93c4cfe07c0d82867df1a511f6fba108e","tid":684751,"uid":182927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T21:43:31.000Z","msg":"好似好正"},{"pid":"befa9c09e323fff98cf38706c1787a0fdf06478a","tid":684751,"uid":10637,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T22:27:15.000Z","msg":"Trailer永遠都係美好<br />\n出到黎會縮哂水"},{"pid":"e4358bb040d1f82c220f89007764e7b38973939a","tid":684751,"uid":46910,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T22:30:37.000Z","msg":"BF 仆街喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12351b1b29b3dab04e3ce351ce8ef421ec708552","tid":684751,"uid":125623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T00:13:14.000Z","msg":"Prepare yourself, war is coming <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2556d66b192e676e5c6013042e6cc2653c96dd97","tid":684751,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T00:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4af6233288d68c2fb52ee0f7f134ff123d1325b","tid":684751,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T00:59:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c607d9c63e983d3f069a6b5041c49421f0403ea3","tid":684751,"uid":21279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T01:04:26.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n睇左完整gameplay先講"},{"pid":"8a35b1679dfce4f203f9ec87cbbdfeae4ad823a6","tid":684751,"uid":143499,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T01:26:14.000Z","msg":"如果呢隻game係玩寫實就好啦， 嗰班支那傻閪就可以理正言順咁玩解放軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應該會畀所有國家虐殺<img src=\"/assets/faces